		{
			dependencies: ["7439F90F2ECE4041"]
			description: [
				"&6&oHere, at the absolute edge of existence, the true source reveals itself. The miasma wasn't a plague—it was breath. The Nightwarden stands over the void, an ancient cosmic entity that orchestrated the Great War from the shadows to feed its own hunger. It is the beginning and the end. Defeating it means breaking the dark cycle and claiming true freedom for the universe.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"The architect of our suffering does not hide anymore. Rend the heavens, and strike a Daemon down.\"&r&r"
			]
