		{
			dependencies: ["79D58811F20E6909"]
			description: [
				"&6&oAs the Nightwarden falls, reality shudders... then exhales. The miasma that plagued the realms begins to dissipate into stardust. The Gate shatters entirely. The Pact of the Gate has fulfilled its impossible task. You stand amidst the silent stars, the ultimate victor of an extinguished cosmos.&r&r"
				""
				"&4&o\"No more rulers. No more corruption. The worlds are finally, truly, our own to rebuild.\"&r&r"
			]
